    <briefdescription>
<para>Uniform random position on a sphere with isotropic Lamberts distributed directions. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This function should be used for crosschecking the arrival distribution for a Galactic propagation with an isotropic arrival distribution at the Edge of our Galaxy. Note, that for simulation speed you should rather use the backtracking technique: see e.g. <ulink url="http://physik.rwth-aachen.de/parsec">http://physik.rwth-aachen.de/parsec</ulink> </para>
    </detaileddescription>
